items.name: EPIK Learning Tab 7" Kids Tablet 16GB Intel Atom Processor Preloaded with Learning Apps & Games
items.shortDescription: The EPIK Learning Intel Quad Core 7" Kids' Tablet brings your child a compact, ultra-portable entertainment device that will let them read email, surf the Internet, read ebooks, view photos, play games, listen to music and watch video files. The tablets are based on a smaller operating system, which allows you to purchase and download additional applications from supported stores for your child to enjoy. They do not have a CD/DVD drive and will not run Microsoft Windows or its applications. They function as a secondary device for casual entertainment purposes and are not meant to replace a computer.
